title: The Party (1968) (Peter Sellers, Claudine Longet)
description:
THE PARTY - 1968

  Peter Sellers stars as a would-be actor from India (let them try to get away with that today) who is a stumbling, bumbling boob. After ruining a day's shooting as an extra on a film, he finds himself unintentionally invited to a big Hollywood party. He's a walking disaster area and the slapstick humor (not easy to keep funny over time) is hilarious.

  Starring: Peter Sellers, Claudine Longet, Natalia Borisova, Jean Carson, Marge Champion.

  Directed by: Blake Edwards.

  Quality: Very Good Xvid from DVD.

  Length: 1hr. 35min.

  Language: English.

  Size: 720 x 336
